overview: Tells the story of Delen a teenager who tries his best to seduce Emily. However, the presence of a new actor, Robert, who has an attractive and handsome personality, has been a hindrance to Delen's efforts.  With the help of Jenny's sister (Sherry) as a love advisor Delen starts competing with Robert to be the best man for Emily.  Although Robert has a very handsome appearance and is the craze of many girls there, Robert still feels Delen as his challenger.  There were various events and competitions to prove who was the most deserving man to own Emily.
title: Delen
